items.title: After bruising election loss, what next for Kamala Harris?
items.description: The outgoing vice-president is weighing her options, which could include another White House run, or a bid to be California's governor.

items.title: Severe winter storm puts much of US on high alert
items.description: Millions of Americans in eastern states brace for blizzards and treacherous ice as a severe winter storm spreads.

items.title: Guatemalan forces arrive in Haiti to fight gangs
items.description: Guatemala sends 150 soldiers to Haiti's capital to help a UN-backed force tackle powerful armed gangs.

items.title: Tanzania's fuel revolution slowed down by lack of filling stations
items.description: The authorities want vehicles to switch to gas but the transition has been hampered by a lack of filling stations.
